<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.5">
<l>cōti yākiyel lāvula kuntoḻu</l>
<l>māti mūrttiyeṉ ṟālaḷa vākumō</l>
<l>vēti yarmuḻu vētat tamutattait</l>
<l>tītil cīrttiru vēṅkaṭat tāṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you call him the primordial form</l>
<l>whom all the worlds worship as light, is it [his] measure,</l>
<l>the one from sacred Vēṅkaṭam of flawless excellence,</l>
<l>the ambrosia of the whole Veda of the Veda experts?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
